# oxfmt reads this file (Prettier convention) — controls files
# excluded from `pnpm format` / `pnpm format:check`.
#
# Markdown is excluded because nested numbered + bulleted lists
# get mangled into single-line continuations during reformat.

*.md
**/*.md

# Generated / vendored
**/dist/**
**/node_modules/**
**/.turbo/**
**/coverage/**
**/playwright-report/**
**/test-results/**

# Go executor (formatted by gofmt, not oxfmt)
executor/**
*.pb.go

# Lockfiles
pnpm-lock.yaml
go.sum
